headline: Industrial Packaging Stocks Q4 Earnings: Sealed Air (NYSE:SEE) Best of the Bunch
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how industrial packaging stocks fared in Q4, starting with Sealed Air (NYSE:SEE).
